        <div class="container">
            <% if(title === "Treasurehunt"){ %>
            <h1 style="color:white">Treasure Hunt:</h1><br>
            <hr > 
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    
                <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/TreasureHunt2.png" width="60%" height="auto">
                    
                 <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                    <p class="about">
                    1)Treasure Hunt is a group event and each participating group can have maximum 3 members<br>
                    2)Each team will be given a hint to spot within campus wherein which the hint for next spot will be hidden.<br>
                    3)The team need to hunt for cascading hints that would eventually lead them to the treasure.<br>
                    4)Only one team amongst many could go home with the treasure. 
                    </p>
            <% } %>   
            
            <%  if(title === "gaming"){ %>
                <h1 style="color:white">Gaming:</h1><br>
                <hr > 
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        
                    <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/gaming.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                        
                     <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                        <p class="about">
                         1) Signup with your teammates to join and play Pubg.<br> 2)A room will be created and id will be circulated to the participants and the game will commence.
                        </p>
                <% } %> 
                
                <%  if(title === "Connexions"){ %>
                    <h1 style="color:white">Connexions:</h1><br>
                    <hr > 
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            
                        <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/conexions post.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                            
                         <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                            <p class="about">
                            1) A group event with maximum 3 members per team.<br>2) Will be provided with a set of connected images that could mean something related to technical concepts or it may be in general.<br>3) The team decrypting and cracking the most answers will be rewarded.
                            </p>
                    <% } %> 
                
                    <%  if(title === "MarvelQuiz"){ %>
                        <h1 style="color:white">Marvel Quiz:</h1><br>
                        <hr > 
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                
                            <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/marvelquiz.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                                
                             <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                                <p class="about">
                                    1) A group event with maximum 3 members per team.<br> 2) Participant will be provided with an ample number of questions that is factually relevant to the Marvel Cinematic Universe.<br>3) The participant answering the most questions within time constraint will be qualified for the next round.   

                                </p>
                        <% } %> 
                    
                        <%  if(title === "IPLAuction"){ %>
                            <h1 style="color:white">IPL Auction:</h1><br>
                            <hr > 
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-lg-6">
                                    
                                <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/IPL Auction.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                                    
                                 <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                                    <p class="about">
                                        Round 1:<br>
                                        Prelims Quiz - General IPL quiz. Only captain of the team can attend the quiz.<br>
                                        Round 2:<br>
                                        1) Each team will be assigned an ipl team on a lottery basis and a purse amount.<br>2) Players list will be casted and can be bid according to the base price.<br>3) Whichever team buys the most balanced and powerful team will be declared the winner.  
    
                                    </p>
                            <% } %> 

                            <%  if(title === "reversecoding"){ %>
                                <h1 style="color:white">Reverse Coding:</h1><br>
                                <hr > 
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                                        
                                    <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/Reverse Coding.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                                        
                                     <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                                        <p class="about">
                                            Reverse coding is a team event of max 3 members where the team will be provided with an IDE to try out various test cases. <br>So the agenda is that the team should come up with the hidden algorithm that provides them the outputs for the respective test cases. You have to crack and code the program that has produced the corresponding outputs.
        
                                        </p>
                                <% } %> 

                                <%  if(title === "Legion"){ %>
                                    <h1 style="color:white">Legion:</h1><br>
                                    <hr > 
                                    <div class="row">
