                                        <img class="cont" src="/images/Assets/legion.png" width="100%" height="auto">
                                            
                                         <h2>Instructions:</h2><br> 
                                            <p class="about">
                                                1) Legion is an exquisite event conducted for the very first time.<br>2) The candidates will be asked to make a group of either 2 or 3 a team.<br>3) Depending on the size of the group, the number of solutions for a problem is validated.<br>4) The teams solving problems in exactly the number of ways that the team size is of proceeds to further levels.
                                            </p>
                                    <% } %> 
